pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Amakuru yerekanwe kuriyi mbaho yakusanyirijwe hamwe mubisubizo byubushakashatsi kandi ntabwo biva mubihugu byemewe mubihugu cyangwa imibare yashizweho. Irerekana ibitekerezo byatanzwe nurubyiruko mugihe cyiperereza, kandi imyanzuro yose yavuye muri ibyo bisubizo ninshingano zumukoresha, ntabwo ari PMNCH. PMNCH yiyemeje kubaha, guteza imbere no kurengera uburenganzira n'imibereho myiza yabantu bose. Igitekerezo icyo ari cyo cyose cyagaragaye mubisubizo byubushakashatsi cyangwa ibikoresho byatangajwe biva muri iki cyicaro kivuguruza iyi mihigo ntabwo byemejwe na PMNCH.

pmn01a-subtext: Murakaza neza kuri "Icyo Urubyiruko Rushaka" Dashboard! Iki gikoresho gikorana gitanga ishusho yerekana ibisubizo nubushishozi dukusanya kuva mu rubyiruko rufite imyaka 10-24 kwisi yose. Intego yibikorwa ni ikibazo gifunguye: "Kugira ngo ubuzima bwanjye burusheho kuba bwiza, ndashaka ...". Urubyiruko ruturutse hirya no hino ku isi rwagiye rusubiza ibi, biduha ubumenyi bwihariye kubyo bakeneye, ibyiringiro, n'ibyifuzo byabo. Shakisha amakuru, umenye inkuru ziri inyuma yimibare, kandi wifatanye natwe mukwongerera amajwi urubyiruko miliyari 1.8 kwisi yose. Kugira ngo umenye byinshi kubyerekeye ubukangurambaga, sura http://www.1 point8.org.
